              "id": "set-welcome",
              "name": "output",
              "value": "👋 Welcome to *Mitra AI*!\n\nI'm your personal AI assistant. Here's what I can help with:\n\n📧 /email - Check & manage emails\n📅 /calendar - Calendar & scheduling\n📁 /docs - Document search & organization\n💰 /budget - Budget tracking & alerts\n💳 /finance - Financial analysis\n❤️ /health - Health monitoring\n🍽️ /calories - Calorie tracking (send food photo!)\n✅ /todo - Task management\n🏃 /fitness - Workout & fitness tracking\n🌟 /motivation - Daily motivation & progress\n\nJust type naturally or send a food photo!",
